node.text:
I’ve included in this video bird of paradise with wall support, as well as standing compass.
I love using the wall as a tool to access a deeper understanding of standing poses, and then applying that new information while standing in my balancing pose. When you use the wall, still keep an awareness on the standing leg - grounding evenly into the foot, contracting the thigh and maintaining stability.
At the end of the video is how I used to use the strap when I was first learning the shoulder rotation!
#yoga #wallstuff
Wearing @aloyoga cargo leggings in bone #sponsored
Song by @danakosber

thank you body for trusting me, for teaching me so much about myself. for allowing me to go inwards and for forgiving me for any criticism or judgment I put you through. you are perfect exactly as you are.
as I breathe in, I invite love, healing and forgiveness into you, and as I breathe out, I am home in my body.
🤍

#loveletterstomybody
#youarebeautiful
#yoga #onebreathatatime 

feel free to share yours with me!! I would love to see it.

I miss the white desert days. i’m writing this in new york as I procrastinate on packing/moving, staring at a huge pile of clothes and shoes that I’m reluctant to keep/too attached to throw, and feeling a huge sense of excitement about our new home— as well as flying back to Egypt for the summer, for new chapters and new beginnings.
the summer for me is always like the restart/reset, when a new year begins and when an old chapter concludes. maybe it’s because my birthday is in august— which season does that for you?
#yoga #summer #egypt #nyc #home
